description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are currently looking for a part time Specialist Therapy Assistant within the Oncology team at Colchester Hospital. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This post (&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;22.5 hours a week Wednesday, Thursday and Friday) &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; will offer an exciting opportunity for an experienced Therapy Assistant. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The successful candidate will have previous experience of working within a therapy service, either in the community or within a hospital setting. Ideally working in or having experience of a palliative setting would be an advantage.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Active participation in current service developments working towards an integrated therapy service is essential.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will need to be highly motivated and show a willingness to develop within the role and participate in Continuing Professional Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will be supported by the Oncology Occupational Therapy and Physiotherapy Team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;There are opportunities for continuing development with access to in-service training, regular supervision and service development.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Come and be a part of our friendly and dynamic team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sarah Marsden Senior Occupational Therapist, on 07776148393&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
